{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":618,"text":"There's this fact that I love\nthat I read somewhere once,"},{"time":3476,"text":"that one of the things that's contributed\nto homo sapiens' success"},{"time":8150,"text":"as a species"},{"time":9517,"text":"is our lack of body hair --"},{"time":11597,"text":"that our hairlessness, our nakedness"},{"time":14045,"text":"combined with our invention of clothing,"},{"time":16375,"text":"gives us the ability to modulate\nour body temperature"},{"time":19693,"text":"and thus be able to survive\nin any climate we choose."},{"time":23797,"text":"And now we've evolved to the point\nwhere we can't survive without clothing."},{"time":27346,"text":"And it's more than just utility,"},{"time":28900,"text":"now it's a communication."},{"time":30245,"text":"Everything that we choose\nto put on is a narrative,"},{"time":33077,"text":"a story about where we've been,"},{"time":35122,"text":"what we're doing,"},{"time":36738,"text":"who we want to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39048,"text":"I was a lonely kid."},{"time":40820,"text":"I didn't have an easy time\nfinding friends to play with,"},{"time":43676,"text":"and I ended up making\na lot of my own play."},{"time":46423,"text":"I made a lot of my own toys."},{"time":48926,"text":"It began with ice cream."},{"time":50589,"text":"There was a Baskin-Robbins in my hometown,"},{"time":53737,"text":"and they served ice cream\nfrom behind the counter"},{"time":56113,"text":"in these giant, five-gallon,\ncardboard tubs."},{"time":58744,"text":"And someone told me --\nI was eight years old --"},{"time":61030,"text":"someone told me that when\nthey were done with those tubs,"},{"time":63754,"text":"they washed them out\nand kept them in the back,"},{"time":65992,"text":"and if you asked they would give you one."},{"time":67970,"text":"It took me a couple of weeks\nto work up the courage,"},{"time":70428,"text":"but I did, and they did."},{"time":71603,"text":"They gave me one -- I went home\nwith this beautiful cardboard tub."},{"time":74940,"text":"I was trying to figure out what\nI could do with this exotic material --"},{"time":78360,"text":"metal ring, top and bottom."},{"time":79769,"text":"I started turning it over in my head,\nand I realized, \"Wait a minute --"},{"time":83178,"text":"my head actually fits inside this thing.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":85344,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86931,"text":"Yeah, I cut a hole out,"},{"time":88648,"text":"I put some acetate in there"},{"time":90191,"text":"and I made myself a space helmet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91929,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":93106,"text":"I needed a place to wear the space helmet,"},{"time":96090,"text":"so I found a refrigerator box\na couple blocks from home."},{"time":98818,"text":"I pushed it home,"},{"time":100129,"text":"and in my parents' guest room closet,"},{"time":102921,"text":"I turned it into a spaceship."},{"time":105336,"text":"I started with a control panel\nout of cardboard."},{"time":107659,"text":"I cut a hole for a radar screen"},{"time":109481,"text":"and put a flashlight\nunderneath it to light it."},{"time":111728,"text":"I put a view screen up,\nwhich I offset off the back wall --"},{"time":114802,"text":"and this is where I thought\nI was being really clever --"},{"time":117459,"text":"without permission, I painted\nthe back wall of the closet black"},{"time":120530,"text":"and put a star field,"},{"time":121713,"text":"which I lit up with some Christmas lights\nI found in the attic,"},{"time":126267,"text":"and I went on some space missions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129214,"text":"A couple years later,"},{"time":130389,"text":"the movie \"Jaws\" came out."},{"time":131815,"text":"I was way too young to see it,\nbut I was caught up in \"Jaws\" fever,"},{"time":135085,"text":"like everyone else in America at the time."},{"time":137709,"text":"There was a store in my town\nthat had a \"Jaws\" costume in their window,"},{"time":141185,"text":"and my mom must have overheard\nme talking to someone"},{"time":143777,"text":"about how awesome\nI thought this costume was,"},{"time":145921,"text":"because a couple days before Halloween,"},{"time":147803,"text":"she blew my freaking mind\nby giving me this \"Jaws\" costume."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152365,"text":"Now, I recognize it's a bit of a trope"},{"time":154789,"text":"for people of a certain age to complain"},{"time":156686,"text":"that kids these days have no idea\nhow good they have it,"},{"time":160246,"text":"but let me just show you a random sampling"},{"time":162315,"text":"of entry-level kids' costumes\nyou can buy online right now ..."},{"time":166037,"text":"... and this is the \"Jaws\" costume\nmy mom bought for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169883,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":172639,"text":"This is a paper-thin shark face"},{"time":175914,"text":"and a vinyl bib with the poster\nof \"Jaws\" on it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179476,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180548,"text":"And I loved it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182411,"text":"A couple years later,"},{"time":183826,"text":"my dad took me to a film\ncalled \"Excalibur.\""},{"time":186667,"text":"I actually got him to take me to it twice,"},{"time":188733,"text":"which is no small thing,\nbecause it is a hard, R-rated film."},{"time":193024,"text":"But it wasn't the blood\nand guts or the boobs"},{"time":195204,"text":"that made me want to go see it again."},{"time":197125,"text":"They helped --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":198307,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":199333,"text":"It was the armor."},{"time":200522,"text":"The armor in \"Excalibur\"\nwas intoxicatingly beautiful to me."},{"time":204660,"text":"These were literally knights\nin shining, mirror-polished armor."},{"time":209301,"text":"And moreover, the knights in \"Excalibur\"\nwear their armor everywhere."},{"time":213502,"text":"All the time -- they wear it at dinner,\nthey wear it to bed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217049,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218124,"text":"I was like, \"Are they reading my mind?"},{"time":220018,"text":"I want to wear armor all the time!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":222510,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223549,"text":"So I went back to my favorite material,"},{"time":225772,"text":"the gateway drug for making,"},{"time":227345,"text":"corrugated cardboard,"},{"time":228789,"text":"and I made myself a suit of armor,"},{"time":231675,"text":"replete with the neck shields\nand a white horse."},{"time":235144,"text":"Now that I've oversold it,"},{"time":236434,"text":"here's a picture of the armor that I made."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238484,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":239849,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":244736,"text":"Now, this is only the first\nsuit of armor I made"},{"time":247351,"text":"inspired by \"Excalibur.\""},{"time":248719,"text":"A couple of years later,"},{"time":249996,"text":"I convinced my dad to embark\non making me a proper suit of armor."},{"time":254118,"text":"Over about a month,"},{"time":255787,"text":"he graduated me from cardboard\nto roofing aluminum called flashing"},{"time":260105,"text":"and still, one of my all-time favorite\nattachment materials,"},{"time":262945,"text":"POP rivets."},{"time":264136,"text":"We carefully, over that month,"},{"time":265872,"text":"constructed an articulated suit\nof aluminum armor"},{"time":268470,"text":"with compound curves."},{"time":269655,"text":"We drilled holes in the helmet\nso that I could breathe,"},{"time":272584,"text":"and I finished just in time\nfor Halloween and wore it to school."},{"time":275655,"text":"Now, this is the one thing in this talk"},{"time":277833,"text":"that I don't have a slide to show you,"},{"time":279674,"text":"because no photo exists of this armor."},{"time":281700,"text":"I did wear it to school,"},{"time":283087,"text":"there was a yearbook photographer\npatrolling the halls,"},{"time":285715,"text":"but he never found me, for reasons\nthat are about to become clear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289129,"text":"There were things I didn't anticipate"},{"time":291231,"text":"about wearing a complete suit\nof aluminum armor to school."},{"time":296061,"text":"In third period math,\nI was standing in the back of class,"},{"time":298846,"text":"and I'm standing in the back of class"},{"time":300671,"text":"because the armor did not\nallow me to sit down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302891,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":304370,"text":"This is the first thing\nI didn't anticipate."},{"time":307351,"text":"And then my teacher looks at me\nsort of concerned"},{"time":309890,"text":"about halfway through the class\nand says, \"Are you feeling OK?\""},{"time":312906,"text":"I'm thinking, \"Are you kidding?\nAm I feeling OK?"},{"time":315176,"text":"I'm wearing a suit of armor!\nI am having the time of my --\""},{"time":318068,"text":"And I'm just about to tell her\nhow great I feel,"},{"time":320752,"text":"when the classroom\nstarts to list to the left"},{"time":323169,"text":"and disappear down this long tunnel,"},{"time":325910,"text":"and then I woke up in the nurse's office."},{"time":330275,"text":"I had passed out from heat exhaustion,"},{"time":333293,"text":"wearing the armor."},{"time":334743,"text":"And when I woke up,"},{"time":335918,"text":"I wasn't embarrassed about having\npassed out in front of my class,"},{"time":339087,"text":"I was wondering, \"Who took my armor?\nWhere's my armor?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":341710,"text":"OK, fast-forward a whole bunch of years,"},{"time":343924,"text":"some colleagues and I get hired\nto make a show for Discovery Channel,"},{"time":347282,"text":"called \"MythBusters.\""},{"time":348457,"text":"And over 14 years,"},{"time":349647,"text":"I learn on the job how to build\nexperimental methodologies"},{"time":352845,"text":"and how to tell stories\nabout them for television."},{"time":355796,"text":"I also learn early on"},{"time":357523,"text":"that costuming can play a key role\nin this storytelling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360406,"text":"I use costumes to add humor, comedy, color"},{"time":364465,"text":"and narrative clarity\nto the stories we're telling."},{"time":367935,"text":"And then we do an episode\ncalled \"Dumpster Diving,\""},{"time":370718,"text":"and I learn a little bit more"},{"time":373009,"text":"about the deeper implications\nof what costuming means to me."},{"time":376464,"text":"In the episode \"Dumpster Diving,\""},{"time":378084,"text":"the question we were trying to answer is:"},{"time":380063,"text":"Is jumping into a dumpster as safe"},{"time":381730,"text":"as the movies would lead you to believe?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":383730,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":385528,"text":"The episode was going to have\ntwo distinct parts to it."},{"time":388187,"text":"One was where we get trained\nto jump off buildings by a stuntman"},{"time":391266,"text":"into an air bag."},{"time":392623,"text":"And the second was the graduation\nto the experiment:"},{"time":395128,"text":"we'd fill a dumpster full of material\nand we'd jump into it."},{"time":397997,"text":"I wanted to visually separate\nthese two elements,"},{"time":400308,"text":"and I thought,"},{"time":401489,"text":"\"Well, for the first part we're training,\nso we should wear sweatsuits --"},{"time":405197,"text":"Oh! Let's put 'Stunt Trainee'\non the back of the sweatsuits."},{"time":408969,"text":"That's for the training.\""},{"time":410337,"text":"But for the second part, I wanted\nsomething really visually striking --"},{"time":413726,"text":"\"I know! I'll dress as Neo\nfrom 'The Matrix.'\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":416228,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":417326,"text":"So I went to Haight Street."},{"time":418660,"text":"I bought some beautiful\nknee-high, buckle boots."},{"time":421263,"text":"I found a long, flowing coat on eBay."},{"time":423729,"text":"I got sunglasses, which I had to wear\ncontact lenses in order to wear."},{"time":427474,"text":"The day of the experiment shoot comes up,"},{"time":429478,"text":"and I step out of my car in this costume,"},{"time":431470,"text":"and my crew takes a look at me ..."},{"time":433990,"text":"and start suppressing\ntheir church giggles."},{"time":436893,"text":"They're like,\n\"(Laugh sound).\""},{"time":440011,"text":"And I feel two distinct things\nat this moment."},{"time":442466,"text":"I feel total embarrassment"},{"time":444187,"text":"over the fact that\nit's so nakedly clear to my crew"},{"time":446957,"text":"that I'm completely\ninto wearing this costume."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449623,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":451328,"text":"But the producer in my mind reminds myself"},{"time":454572,"text":"that in the high-speed shot in slow-mo,"},{"time":457023,"text":"that flowing coat is going to look\nbeautiful behind me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":460140,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":462012,"text":"Five years into the \"MythBusters\" run,"},{"time":463907,"text":"we got invited to appear\nat San Diego Comic-Con."},{"time":466587,"text":"I'd known about Comic-Con for years\nand never had time to go."},{"time":470007,"text":"This was the big leagues --\nthis was costuming mecca."},{"time":473635,"text":"People fly in from all over the world"},{"time":475699,"text":"to show their amazing creations\non the floor in San Diego."},{"time":478845,"text":"And I wanted to participate."},{"time":480394,"text":"I decided that I would put together\nan elaborate costume"},{"time":483480,"text":"that covered me completely,"},{"time":484938,"text":"and I would walk the floor\nof San Diego Comic-Con anonymously."},{"time":488581,"text":"The costume I chose?"},{"time":489923,"text":"Hellboy."},{"time":491493,"text":"That's not my costume,"},{"time":492668,"text":"that's actually Hellboy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493843,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":494886,"text":"But I spent months"},{"time":496068,"text":"assembling the most screen-accurate\nHellboy costume I could,"},{"time":498932,"text":"from the boots to the belt to the pants"},{"time":500891,"text":"to the right hand of doom."},{"time":502303,"text":"I found a guy who made\na prosthetic Hellboy head and chest"},{"time":505718,"text":"and I put them on."},{"time":507031,"text":"I even had contact lenses made\nin my prescription."},{"time":510786,"text":"I wore it onto the floor at Comic-Con"},{"time":513140,"text":"and I can't even tell you\nhow balls hot it was in that costume."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517793,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":518857,"text":"Sweating! I should've remembered this."},{"time":520916,"text":"I'm sweating buckets\nand the contact lenses hurt my eyes,"},{"time":523829,"text":"and none of it matters\nbecause I'm totally in love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527402,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":529066,"text":"Not just with the process of putting\non this costume and walking the floor,"},{"time":532653,"text":"but also with the community\nof other costumers."},{"time":536256,"text":"It's not called costuming at Cons,"},{"time":538176,"text":"it's called \"cosplay.\""},{"time":540026,"text":"Now ostensibly, cosplay means\npeople who dress up"},{"time":542574,"text":"as their favorite characters\nfrom film and television"},{"time":545161,"text":"and especially anime,"},{"time":546369,"text":"but it is so much more than that."},{"time":549134,"text":"These aren't just people\nwho find a costume and put it on --"},{"time":552219,"text":"they mash them up."},{"time":553640,"text":"They bend them to their will."},{"time":555124,"text":"They change them to be the characters\nthey want to be in those productions."},{"time":558940,"text":"They're super clever and genius."},{"time":560880,"text":"They let their freak flag fly\nand it's beautiful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563567,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":564630,"text":"But more than that,"},{"time":565805,"text":"they rehearse their costumes."},{"time":567282,"text":"At Comic-Con or any other Con,"},{"time":568782,"text":"you don't just take pictures\nof people walking around."},{"time":571353,"text":"You go up and say,"},{"time":572532,"text":"\"Hey, I like your costume,\ncan I take your picture?\""},{"time":575008,"text":"And then you give them time\nto get into their pose."},{"time":577828,"text":"They've worked hard on their pose"},{"time":579522,"text":"to make their costume look\ngreat for your camera."},{"time":582166,"text":"And it's so beautiful to watch."},{"time":585178,"text":"And I take this to heart."},{"time":586633,"text":"At subsequent Cons,"},{"time":588163,"text":"I learn Heath Ledger's shambling walk\nas the Joker from \"The Dark Knight.\""},{"time":592580,"text":"I learn how to be a scary Ringwraith\nfrom \"Lord of the Rings,\""},{"time":595654,"text":"and I actually frighten some children."},{"time":597739,"text":"I learned that \"hrr hrr hrr\" --"},{"time":599663,"text":"that head laugh that Chewbacca does."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602625,"text":"And then I dressed up as\nNo-Face from \"Spirited Away.\""},{"time":605623,"text":"If you don't know about \"Spirited Away\"\nand its director, Hayao Miyazaki,"},{"time":609098,"text":"first of all, you're welcome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610573,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":612136,"text":"This is a masterpiece,\nand one of my all-time favorite films."},{"time":615600,"text":"It's about a young girl named Chihiro\nwho gets lost in the spirit world"},{"time":619967,"text":"in an abandoned Japanese theme park."},{"time":622324,"text":"And she finds her way back out again"},{"time":624244,"text":"with the help of a couple\nof friends she makes --"},{"time":626584,"text":"a captured dragon named Haku"},{"time":628098,"text":"and a lonely demon named No-Face."},{"time":630386,"text":"No-Face is lonely\nand he wants to make friends,"},{"time":633280,"text":"and he thinks the way to do it\nis by luring them to him"},{"time":636469,"text":"and producing gold in his hand."},{"time":638563,"text":"But this doesn't go very well,"},{"time":640338,"text":"and so he ends up going\non kind of a rampage"},{"time":643179,"text":"until Chihiro saves him,"},{"time":645459,"text":"rescues him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647081,"text":"So I put together a No-Face costume,"},{"time":650731,"text":"and I wore it on the floor at Comic-Con."},{"time":653012,"text":"And I very carefully practiced\nNo-Face's gestures."},{"time":657757,"text":"I resolved I would not speak\nin this costume at all."},{"time":661395,"text":"When people asked to take my picture,"},{"time":663458,"text":"I would nod"},{"time":665107,"text":"and I would shyly stand next to them."},{"time":667552,"text":"They would take the picture"},{"time":669242,"text":"and then I would secret out\nfrom behind my robe"},{"time":671980,"text":"a chocolate gold coin."},{"time":673526,"text":"And at the end of the photo process,\nI'd make it appear for them."},{"time":676918,"text":"Ah, ah ah! -- like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":679651,"text":"And people were freaking out."},{"time":681058,"text":"\"Holy crap! Gold from No-Face!\nOh my god, this is so cool!\""},{"time":684115,"text":"And I'm feeling and I'm walking\nthe floor and it's fantastic."},{"time":688006,"text":"And about 15 minutes in something happens."},{"time":691368,"text":"Somebody grabs my hand,"},{"time":694014,"text":"and they put a coin back into it."},{"time":696116,"text":"And I think maybe they're giving me\na coin as a return gift,"},{"time":699336,"text":"but no, this is one of the coins\nthat I'd given away."},{"time":702229,"text":"I don't know why."},{"time":703704,"text":"And I keep on going,\nI take some more pictures."},{"time":705976,"text":"And then it happens again."},{"time":707939,"text":"Understand, I can't see anything\ninside this costume."},{"time":711174,"text":"I can see through the mouth --"},{"time":712685,"text":"I can see people's shoes."},{"time":714328,"text":"I can hear what they're saying\nand I can see their feet."},{"time":717167,"text":"But the third time someone\ngives me back a coin,"},{"time":719461,"text":"I want to know what's going on."},{"time":721612,"text":"So I sort of tilt my head back\nto get a better view,"},{"time":724695,"text":"and what I see is someone walking\naway from me going like this."},{"time":730271,"text":"And then it hits me:"},{"time":732600,"text":"it's bad luck to take gold from No-Face."},{"time":736257,"text":"In the film \"Spirited Away,\""},{"time":738193,"text":"bad luck befalls those\nwho take gold from No-Face."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742351,"text":"This isn't a performer-audience\nrelationship; this is cosplay."},{"time":749855,"text":"We are, all of us on that floor,"},{"time":752092,"text":"injecting ourselves into a narrative\nthat meant something to us."},{"time":755763,"text":"And we're making it our own."},{"time":757632,"text":"We're connecting with something\nimportant inside of us."},{"time":762333,"text":"And the costumes\nare how we reveal ourselves"},{"time":766116,"text":"to each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767984,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":769164,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}